snippet.title: (DOWNLOAD NOW) Sonic Frontiers Recreation for SRB2 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
this is a map project i've been working on in Sonic Robo Blast 2, and now i want to share it with everyone, download it!

look the whole folder, cause it comes with a level map for make it easier to someone, there are 2 versions 
1 just have the island form and altitude
2 have the location of chaos emeralds, master emeralds and cyberspace levels

Downloads
MEGA: https://mega.nz/file/VTE2ACqR#vpoOzQ3lLODivULeBNzDG6uEh84J89qO34PztrLRpg0
GAMEJOLT: https://gamejolt.com/games/Sonicfrontiersrecreation/754009

#sonic #sonicthehedgehog #sonicfrontiers #sonicroboblast2
